title: #92Noon!  9am Hour 8/15 - Vikings/Raiders, Pete Bercich
description: PA opens the show breaking down some of the standout performances in the Vikings game against the Raiders.  Vikings radio analyst Pete Bercich joins 92Noon to talk Kellen Mond, the Vikes crowded RB room, & more!
